I&#39;m new here and just chiming in with my two cents....

As a practicing medium I do believe Spirits get stuck.  There is a different
energetic feeling I receive when connecting with someone who has truly
crossed over and is now &quot;in spirit&quot; versus someone who has not.   Those who
are stuck either do not realize they have died or they are attached to our
Earth plane (be it a particular person or event) and don&#39;t want to or know
how to leave.  I believe it is those stuck individuals who are often behind
the rattle & clatter in hauntings---although this topic is still new to me.

For those who have actually crossed over (and I believe this is the majority
of souls), they return to Spirit and become the light & love they came
from.  Spirits have much better things to do than haunt us, they continue to
learn and evolve on the other side.  However, they do enjoy communicating
with us, especially letting their loved ones know they are ok.

Best,
Alyson



